messages.message: Cross-post from <#CGQ7BD72A|> - reminder that the next code cut and UAT is this coming Monday Nov 9.  Note that this is likely the last release customers will get take this year before the holidays kick in. Please make sure to get your code in beforehand and take a bit more time for UATs since shipping them patches will be harder.
whoa... the November release is upon us. Remember to tag the Jiras with the Fix Version and select docs and release notes.
